<li>Typhimurium pathogenesis CueR belongs to the MerR-family of transcriptional regulators , other members of which regulate cellular homeostasis of other metal ions , free radicals , and small organic molecules ( Ahmed et al. , 1994 ; Pomposiello and Demple , 2001 ; Chen and He , 2008 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21722794" target="_blank">21722794</a>]<br></li>
