<li>We have recently shown that Salmonella has a second CueR homologue highly sensitive to gold ions , GolS , which induces the expression of a CopA-homologous protein , GolT , and a putative metal-binding protein , GolB ( Checa et al. , 2007 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=17768242" target="_blank">17768242</a>]<br></li>
